data.description: Step into this beautiful Spacious 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom, 2-Car garage Merritt Island home with a Bonus Room perfect for an office or extra bedroom. A/C 2023( inside/out), New Roof to be replaced 1/2024! New Pipes 2023, H/W 2023, Irrigation Pump 2023, Water Softener throughout home...just add salt. Hot tub negotiable with 2 yr warranty. This home boasts a HUGE Family room perfect for gatherings and lasting memories. Great kitchen with ample counter space, and plenty of storage for all your culinary needs. Splish splash fun in the sun or relax by the inviting pool with a book or drink in hand. Versatile shed with great storage potential, ideal for anyone in need of extra space. The driveway is spacious enough to accommodate an RV/Boat. Ideal location close to three schools, dining, shops and the beach! Schedule a private showing today! The other two bedrooms nice size with great closet space. New Pipes. Close to Schools, Dining/Shops. Schedule Private showing today!
